---
layout: default
---

<div class="relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-1/2"></div>
  <div class="relative sm:overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      {% imageHome "./assets/images/home.jpg", "Home BG", "Home BG" %}
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:py-32 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-center text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        <span class="block text-white">{{ title }}</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg mx-auto text-center text-xl text-white sm:max-w-3xl">
        If you love to learn, you are in the right place.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-gray-50 dark:text-gray-50 inline-flex items-center mx-4 no-underline hover:underline">Blog
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            fill="currentColor"
            class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 bi bi-chevron-right"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1
                0-.708z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/wiki" class="text-gray-50 dark:text-gray-50 inline-flex items-center mx-4 no-underline hover:underline">Wiki
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            fill="currentColor"
            class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 bi bi-chevron-right"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1
                0-.708z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:pb-28 lg:px-8">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="h-1/3 sm:h-2/3"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mt-12 max-w-lg mx-auto grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:max-w-none">
      <div class="flex flex-col rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          {% image "./assets/images/projects.jpg", "Projects BG", "Projects BG" %}
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white dark:bg-black p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
              Projects
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              Learn more about my projects. They can be of any kind but I am more interested in Python or web
              developpement. If you ever want to propose me an exciting project, feel free to contact me !
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex">
            <a
              href="/projects/"
              class="px-5 py-2 font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 transform rounded-md text-gray-50 bg-blue-600
                hover:bg-blue-500">
              Discover my projects
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          {% image "./assets/images/writing.jpg", "Writing BG", "Writing BG" %}
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white dark:bg-black p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
              Books
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              Learn more about what I am writing. It can be about anything I want to write about but I do prefer the novels and books.
              If you have any comments about my writing, please let me know !
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex">
            <a
              href="/books/"
              class="px-5 py-2 font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 transform rounded-md text-gray-50 bg-blue-600
                hover:bg-blue-500">
              Discover my books
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          {% image "./assets/images/games.jpg", "Games BG", "Games BG" %}
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white dark:bg-black p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
              Games
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              Learn more about the games I play everyday. From tabletop to video games, I play a large range of games. I am also a
              member of a gaming association, so if you are interested, join us !
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex">
            <a
              href="/games/"
              class="px-5 py-2 font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 transform rounded-md text-gray-50 bg-blue-600
                hover:bg-blue-500">
              Discover my games
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>